{"CURMUDGEON":[{"def":"An avaricious, grasping fellow; a miser; a niggard; a churl.","pos":""}],"CURMUDGEONLY":[{"def":"Like a curmudgeon; niggardly; churlish; as, a curmudgeonly fellow.","pos":""}],"CURMURRING":[{"def":"Murmuring; grumbling; -- sometimes applied to the rumbling produced by a slight attack of the gripes.","pos":""}]}